title: Tuesdays With Morrie 1999 XviD AC3.2CD-WAF
description:
Tuesdays With Morrie 1999 XviD AC3.2CD-WAF

Mitch became caught up with his career as a sport commentator and journalist. He ignored his girlfriend and did not make time to do things in life that are of the most value to a human being. Morrie was one of Mitch's professors in college and a famous scholar. One day Mitch was watching television and saw Morrie giving an interview stating that he is dying of Lou Gehrig disease or ALS. Written by Rosemea D.S. MacPherson
